  "description": "Spawns a random mob when you break a block.",
  "body": "<a href=\"fabricmc.net\">\n  <img src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.jsdelivr.net%2Fnpm%2F%40intergrav%2Fdevins-badges%402.8.0%2Fassets%2Fcozy%2Fsupported%2Ffabric_vector.svg&n=-1\" alt=\"For Fabric Loader\" style=\"width:42px;height:42px;\">\n</a> \n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/fabric-api\">\n  <img src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.jsdelivr.net%2Fnpm%2F%40intergrav%2Fdevins-badges%402.8.0%2Fassets%2Fcozy%2Frequires%2Ffabric-api_vector.svg&n=-1\" alt=\"Requires Fabric API\" style=\"width:42px;height:42px;\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/randommobblock\">\n  <img src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.jsdelivr.net%2Fnpm%2F%40intergrav%2Fdevins-badges%402.8.0%2Fassets%2Fcozy%2Favailable%2Fmodrinth_vector.svg&n=-1\" alt=\"Avaible on Modrinth\" style=\"width:42px;height:42px;\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/randommobblock\">\n  <img src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.jsdelivr.net%2Fnpm%2F%40intergrav%2Fdevins-badges%402.8.0%2Fassets%2Fcozy%2Favailable%2Fcurseforge_vector.svg&n=-1\" alt=\"Avaible on Curseforge\" style=\"width:42px;height:42px;\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/theanonym3000\">\n  <img src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.jsdelivr.net%2Fnpm%2F%40intergrav%2Fdevins-badges%402.8.0%2Fassets%2Fcozy%2Fsocial%2Fgithub-singular_vector.svg&n=-1\" alt=\"See me on GitHub\" style=\"width:42px;height:42px;\">\n</a>\n\nSpawns a random mob when you break a block.\nUses SQLite JDBC to save the mob to the block.\n\nSQLite JDBC has to be installed! Modrinth says that it is incompatible with 1.21.4, but it is compatible!\n\nThanks to:\nR40fendt for the help with the database!\nSnow_Wars for the idea!",
